These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, jazz, metal, soul
1. the fan of jazz is between the fan of metal and the fan of soul##2
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | soul | jazz | metal |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda | cola | iced-tea |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | bird | turtle | pony | ferret |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, nectarine, papaya, strawberry
1. the person eating papaya is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating asparagus##2
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | strawberry | nectarine | papaya | asparagus |

 #################################
 
